# Inventory Discrepancy Reporting — RGIS

Structured inventory audit and variance reporting across client sites.

## Overview
At RGIS Manchester (2022–2023), I executed precision inventory audits for retail and warehouse clients. This repository documents the audit methodology, discrepancy reporting structure, and data integrity workflows applied across multiple client engagements.

## Tools Used
- RGIS proprietary audit systems
- Excel (variance reporting)
- Manual count verification

## Audit Workflow
```
1. Pre-audit setup     → Download expected counts
2. Physical count      → Scan & record actual stock
3. Variance detection  → Flag SKUs with discrepancy
4. Root cause review   → Identify source of variance
5. Resolution report   → Submit findings to client
```

